{"id": 1669, "genre": 1000, "title": "如今各个领域都在瞎用哪些“降维”？", "description": "升维降维张口就来，刘慈欣看了想打人。（题图来自：giphy）", "record_count": 5751, "comment_count": 43, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170506122231nMoCq5T4jWatB1RD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-10T17:00:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 2273, "title": "如今各个领域都在瞎用哪些“降维”？", "content": "如今各个领域都在瞎用哪些“降维”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 200892, "content": "阅读降维，深度内容“降维”为碎片化，以帮助读者更好地…不思考吗", "image": "img/option/option/20170506123336OevGkolH3pJaKTQZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 200893, "content": "B站日剧资源下线，叫做遭遇了从三次元降到二次元的“降维打击”", "image": "img/option/option/20170506123812sadeotuUwl5LfiET.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 200896, "content": "做电影的人做综艺，对其他综艺是“降维攻击”…你是想说碾压吧？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506145228ilSRaGPjJkV2nNOq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 200997, "content": "游戏先发主机再发Steam和手机端，也叫降维，咋就降维了？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506145301rYXkNdajHDLAR3pm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 200999, "content": "“大家都做贵的，我做便宜的”叫降维攻击…不就是价格战吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506145534zIojYqsbkdA0EWmD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201000, "content": "“大家都做便宜的，我做个贵的”也叫降维，前不久不还叫互联网思维？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506150916wZGAeOior73Q8mjY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201001, "content": "微信转型做内容，对其他软件是“降维打击”，微信人多势众就高人一维？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506151109xmiOMVUgWRJyFacv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201002, "content": "“升维思考，降维打击”，互联网时代不懂这个你就输了……？？？", "image": "img/option/option/20170506151120v6CHFAYlRB4rOkPI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}